  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Driftwood Piece</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Driftwood Pieces</b> are <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Items\" title=\"Items\">Items</a> exclusive to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i>, introduced in <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Return_of_Them\" title=\"Return of Them\">Return of Them</a></i>.\n</p><p>They can be found floating in the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ocean\" title=\"Ocean\">Ocean</a> where they spawn <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ocean_Debris\" title=\"Ocean Debris\">regularly</a>. They are common in the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rocky_Beach\" title=\"Rocky Beach\">Rocky Beach</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Biomes\" title=\"Biomes\">Biome</a> on the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Island\" title=\"Lunar Island\">Lunar Island</a>. Driftwood Pieces can also be obtained by chopping <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Driftwood\" title=\"Driftwood\">Driftwood</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Great_Tree_Trunk\" title=\"Great Tree Trunk\">Great Tree Trunk</a> roots.\n</p><p>Driftwood Pieces are required to craft <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Driftwood_Oar\" title=\"Driftwood Oar\">Driftwood Oars</a>. They can also be used to repair <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Boat_Kit\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Boat Kit\">Boats</a> and as <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fuel\" title=\"Fuel\">Fuel</a> for <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fire\" title=\"Fire\">Fire</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Driftwood_Piece\" title=\"Driftwood Piece\"><img alt=\"Driftwood Piece.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Driftwood_Piece.png?4006fa\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><img alt=\"Interface arrow right.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Interface_arrow_right.png/42px-Interface_arrow_right.png?d3cbb3\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Driftwood_Oar\" title=\"Driftwood Oar\"><img alt=\"Driftwood Oar.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Driftwood_Oar.png?846f6d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Driftwood_Piece\" title=\"Driftwood Piece\"><img alt=\"Driftwood Piece.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Driftwood_Piece.png?4006fa\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tackle_Receptacle\" title=\"Tackle Receptacle\"><img alt=\"Tackle Receptacle.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Tackle_Receptacle.png/42px-Tackle_Receptacle.png?409a77\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hardened_Slip_Bobber\" title=\"Hardened Slip Bobber\"><img alt=\"Hardened Slip Bobber.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Hardened_Slip_Bobber.png?38b6d7\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></t