  "wikitext": "{{Object Infobox\n|foodType =[[Food_Type#Wood|Wood]] [[File:Wood_Type_Icon.png|25px|link=Food_Type#Wood]]<br>(non-survivor food)\n|icon = Driftwood Piece.png\n|image = Driftwood Piece Dropped.png\n|hpRestored = 0\n|hungerRestored = 0\n|sanityRestored = 0\n|canBeBurned=1\n|burnTime = [[File:Light_Sources_Filter.png|32px|link=Fuel#Fire Fuel]] 45 sec.\n|stack = 20\n|droppedBy = {{Pic|32|Driftwood 1|Driftwood}}  {{Pic|24|Great_Tree_Root_1|Great_Tree_Trunk}}  ({{pic|24|Axe}})<br> {{pic|32|Marotter Den}}\n|spawnCode = \"driftwood_log\"}}{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve Together}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = It floats on water.\n|willow = Perfect for burning.\n|wolfgang = Small log is practically fit in palm of my hand!\n|wendy = Bleached like bones left in the sun.\n|wx78 = TREEFRAGMENTED.\n|wickerbottom = A naturally buoyant material.\n|woodie = You poor log.\n|maxwell = Oh good. More wood.\n|wigfrid = 'Tis wĂ¶Ă¶d, fĂ¶rged in the sea's depths!\n|webber = Easy piece-y.\n|winona = Oof. Kitschy.\n|warly = It's surprisingly light.\n|wortox = Naught but a log.\n|wormwood = Going for swim, friend?\n|wurt = Floaty log.\n|walter = You'll float too, if you hold onto it!\n|wanda = Who knows how long it's been floating out in the ocean?\n|choose = wigfrid}}\n'''Driftwood Pieces''' are [[Items]] exclusive to ''[[Don't Starve Together]]'', introduced in ''[[Return of Them]]''.\n\nThey can be found floating in the [[Ocean]] where they spawn [[Ocean Debris|regularly]]. They are common in the [[Rocky Beach]] [[Biomes|Biome]] on the [[Lunar Island]]. Driftwood Pieces can also be obtained by chopping [[Driftwood]] and [[Great Tree Trunk]] roots.\n\nDriftwood Pieces are required to craft [[Driftwood Oar]]s. They can also be used to repair [[Boat Kit|Boats]] and as [[Fuel]] for [[Fire]].\n\n== {{Pic32|Icon Tools}} Usage==\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Driftwood Piece\n|count1=1\n|result=Driftwood Oar}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Driftwood Piece\n|result = Hardened Slip Bobber\n|tool = Tackle Receptacle}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Driftwood Piece\n|count1 = 4\n|tool = Sawhorse\n|result = Driftwood Rocker\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Driftwood Piece\n|item2 = Rocks\n|tool = Terra Firma Tamper\n|result = Rocky Beach Turf\n|resultcount = 4\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Driftwood Piece\n|count1 = 1\n|item2 = Electrical Doodad\n|count2 = 1\n|item3 = Bone Shards\n|count3 = 1\n|result = Tackle Receptacle\n|tool = Science Machine}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Rope\n|count2 = 1\n|item1 = Driftwood Piece\n|count1 = 2\n|item3 = Malbatross Bill\n|count3 = 1\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Waterfowl Can\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Driftwood Piece\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Rope\n|count2 = 3\n|item3 = Feathery Canvas\n|count3 = 4\n|result = Winged Sail\n|tool = Think Tank}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Driftwood Piece\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Barnacles\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Rope/DST\n|count3 = 3\n|tool = Crabby Hermit\n|result = Large Drying Rack\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Driftwood Piece\n|item2 = Marsh Turf\n|item3 = Pure Horror\n|result = Dreaded Mudslinger\n|character = Wurt\n|skill = Terra Corruption\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Driftwood Piece\n|item2 = Marsh Turf\n|item3 = Pure Brilliance\n|result = Brilliant Mudslinger\n|character = Wurt\n|skill = Terra Mutation\n}}\n\n== {{Pic|32|Placeholder}} Trivia ==\n* Driftwood Pieces were introduced in the ''[[Return of Them#Turn of Tides|Turn of Tides]]'' update.\n\n\n{{Resources}}\n[[vi:Driftwood Piece]]\n[[Category:Return of Them]]\n[[Category:Resources]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]\n[[Category:Fuel]]\n[[Category:Non-Renewable]]"
